---
title: Smokey Crumbed Chicken Tacos with Charred Corn Slaw & Spring Onion
description: Crispy crumbed chicken, creamy slaw and charred corn in a taco – we promise, this combo is love at first bite! And second bite, and third bite...
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6539f26871c23d86f5f00875-06daeff8.jpeg
